                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">To clear it up: no, not all charmed pets are dualwielding.
<br />
It is indeed class dependend too. You wont have a cleric
<br />
pet that is dualwielding or an enchanter. If you have a 
<br />
warrior, no doubt it usually can. Be aware that certain mob
<br />
names or mob titles are not giving the full explanation what 
<br />
class the mob represents, but usually it is correct.
<br />

<br />
Some mobs are using a kind of internal dualwielding
<br />
already - say a monster can bite and kick (e.g. horses).
<br />
Those wont possibly accept weapons at all. Just read
<br />
their emotions. If they wont change to the weapon
<br />
specific emotions, they wont use them.
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">My advice: </span>
<br />

<br />
You can always try to give your pet two class dependend weapons.
<br />

<br />
Do not use weapons of the same kind / delay, otherwise most higher level
<br />
pets will only replace the first given weapon then.
<br />

<br />
A 1h sword (slashing emotion) and a 1h dagger (piercing emotion) is nice.
<br />
Be aware that you will kinda doubling the dps with a dualwielding pet.
<br />

<br />
You will get interrupted twice often as normal, if you try to mez / recharm your 
<br />
dualwielding pet. If you can't handle it, dont give your pet 2 weapons at all.
<br />
Same is valid for the haste buff. Even more nice & hard is a hasted
<br />
dualwielding killer pet. Get your own experiences to see how you can
<br />
deal with it.
<br />

<br />
Caster pets prefer daggers or blunt weapons, melee pets take swords and others. 
<br />
Prevent 2h weapons. But a 2h weapon is better than none  <img src="images/smiles/icon_twisted.gif" alt="icon_twisted.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-size: 9px; line-height: normal"><span style="color: darkblue"><a href="http://www.therunes.net/forums/viewtopic.php?p=18979" target="_blank" class="postlink">E65.450/KB h-- 4.5khp 6.2km ft18 G!++++ e++++ 
<br />
o++ T++++ L+(++) H-(++) g++ b c+++++ t+ D- X+@</a></span></span>
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Ompy Trompe</span>, Coercer
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Keeper of the Secrets</span>
