                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">While I haven't seen cast time decreased, my clickies are affected by range extensions.
<br />
When using Memory, for example, I can inch toward a mob until I'm in range for it to work... but then if I take off my range extention foci, I'm out of range once again.
<br />

<br />
Cast time does seem pretty fixed for clickies, but duration and range seem to be influenced.  (I'm not 100% sure on duration, I've yet to do solid testing on it, that is just my impression.)</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=378985" target="_blank" class="postlink">Tashim</a>, 65th Enchanter
