                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Hold the phone here a moment folks.
<br />

<br />
A) Isn't DC level capped?  Ie: it only works on mobs up to level 46?  If I'm wrong on this than the rest of this is garbage, if I'm write then read on (either way, some edification is greatly appreciated).
<br />

<br />
B) Assuming A) what would a 65 want to DC in the zones s/he is normally going to hunt in for exp?  Farm, sure, hunt for exp?  No.
<br />

<br />
