<br />
(and you can take AFKs without worrying about charm breaks)
<br />

<br />
its more damage than a necro or mage pet
<br />

<br />

<br />
you take no exp loss from DC because the lvl 65 group easily outdamages the pet
<br />

<br />

<br />
I've had 2 hasted DC pets in Valor (in 6 person group)
<br />
-- experience was 1 aa per 50min
<br />

<br />

